; Rainbow Spiral
; An expanding square spiral that cycles through all 256
; palette colors twice. Turning 91 degrees per step (just
; over a right angle) causes the shape to slowly rotate,
; filling the canvas with a dense rainbow weave.

HIDETURTLE
SETPENSIZE 2
PENDOWN

FOR [i 0 511] [
  SETPENCOLOR REMAINDER :i 256
  FORWARD :i / 2
  RIGHT 91
]
